Adds additional color combinations to randomly generated weapons.

Do not use at the same time as the Core version of this mod.
Does not add any new colors, just new combinations of existing colors.
This can be used as a tool for easily adding new color options to generated weapons, a sample patch and guide will be published to the forums.
This version keeps all weapon rarities generating from the same color files, so there is no difference aesthetically between them.

